c: 8
v: 67
t: "la yanbaghi linabiin 'an yakun lah 'asraa min aedayh hataa ybalgh fi alqtl; li'iidkhal alrueb fi qulubihim wywtd deaym aldyn, turidun -ya maeshar almslmyn- bakhdhkm alfda' min 'asraa \"bdr\" matae aldnya, wallah yurid 'iizhar dinih aldhy bih tudrik alakhr. wallah eaziz la yuqhr, hakim fi shreh"